            "notes": "The deck focuses on utilizing Aragorn, King of Gondor as the commander to lead an aggressive strategy, combining small creatures with powerful spells to control the game and quickly overwhelm the opponent. It includes a mix of removal spells like Lightning Bolt and Swords to Plowshares, counter spells like Force of Negation and Mana Leak, and powerful creatures like Vendilion Clique and Murktide Regent. The deck aims to apply pressure early on while maintaining control of the game through disruption and card advantage, allowing Aragorn to lead the charge and secure victory. This aggressive tempo strategy requires precise decision-making and efficient resource management to outmaneuver opponents and claim victory on the battlefield."
