            "notes": "The deck focuses on controlling the game by disrupting opponents' strategies through a combination of counterspells, removal spells, and hand disruption. Tasigur, the Golden Fang, serves as the commander, providing card advantage and recursion for valuable spells in the graveyard. The deck includes a variety of versatile spells such as Cryptic Command and Demonic Tutor to handle different situations. It also features cards like Drown in the Loch and Fatal Push for creature removal, ensuring board control. The mana base is designed to support the deck's control elements, with lands like Underground Sea and Watery Grave providing the necessary colors of mana. Overall, the deck aims to outvalue opponents and maintain control of the game until securing a win condition."
